/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a4624ecbf7ab4874e7b7af76424fdf87215d2f","tid":2302451,"uid":127269,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"你地揸就爽 我地駝住兩包米有幾辛苦<br />\n你知咩 你唔知<br />\n因為你只諗到你自己"},{"pid":"8d93f06a3677ac63b8e1d79aa4868456dbb2783c","tid":2302451,"uid":31542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"巨胸版就<br />\n莫說青山多障礙<br />\n搓也得 胸夠勁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ed2ede426a7cd16b9cfdde83a3567309f9899f","tid":2302451,"uid":358948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"都係巨胸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試下唔好淨係講"},{"pid":"7271cf6692613ecb7316b2a980966bed08b98b5e","tid":2302451,"uid":119610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjGkgk9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjGkgk9.gif&h=0a87ef90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXwoYzu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXwoYzu.gif&h=98f09368&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Avcb7sQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvcb7sQ.gif&h=77328446&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGrgy7R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGrgy7R.gif&h=b9ab6cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱啱搵完樓豬條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}